(34, 13, 'Sidu', 'A steamed bread made from wheat flour, which is usually served with ghee or chutney. Sidu is a popular dish in Himachal Pradesh, especially during festivals and family gatherings.', '../Image/HimachalPradesh/Sidu.jpg'),
(35, 13, 'Chana Madra', 'A delicious curry made from chickpeas and yogurt, flavored with aromatic spices. This dish is a staple in Himachal and is usually eaten with steamed rice.', '../Image/HimachalPradesh/ChanaMadra.webp');
