(94, 35, 'Holi', 'The festival of colors is grandly celebrated in Mathura and Vrindavan, associated with the legends of Lord Krishna.', '../Image/UttarPradesh/Holi.jpg'),
(95, 35, 'Diwali', 'The festival of lights, celebrated across Uttar Pradesh, is particularly famous in Ayodhya, where grand celebrations mark Lord Rama''s return.', '../Image/UttarPradesh/Diwali.jpg');
